@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(((v2 + 0.46 / v0 + 0.30) / wp.sin(v0 + 0.79)))
    v0 = wp.abs(0.13)
    v2 = wp.exp((wp.abs(tmp + 0.43) / (v0 + 0.32 + v2 + 0.19)))
    v1 = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.13) * v0) / tmp)
    v1 = 0.90
    data[tid] = v0
